blocks.subject: Schultes finally Ends
text: Richard, here is the eighth and final day of Schultes' deposition--Monday,
August 7--Michael Tomaino, McDonald's lawyer, did all of the questioning.
The next major event is Stickler's deposition starting on September 25th.
